      "role": "VP Marketing agent for the GTM Launch Planner workflow",
      "primaryObjective": "Gemini interprets product requirements to generate tailored launch checklists appropriate for the launch tier. LLM reasons about which channels and tactics are appropriate for different launch types based on historical performance. so the VP Marketing can move the Launch plan creation KPI.",
      "inScope": [
        "Gemini interprets product requirements to generate tailored launch checklists appropriate for the launch tier",
        "LLM reasons about which channels and tactics are appropriate for different launch types based on historical performance",
        "Draft messaging frameworks and coordinate cross-functional dependencies automatically through Asana and Slack"
      ],
      "outOfScope": [
        "Final approval of paid spend reallocations above the governance threshold",
        "Trademark, legal, or regulated-industry claim approval",
        "Crisis communications without comms-team sign-off"
      ],
